snippet.title: Deadlink - Console Launch Trailer (PS5/Xbox Series)
snippet.description:
Deadlink launches on PlayStation 5 on July 30th and Xbox Series on July 31st!

Come check out our launch trailer and pre-order the game at a discounted price:
- https://store.playstation.com/concept/10010769
- https://www.xbox.com/games/store/deadlink/9mx7952w6psq
